OUr GLOBAL REACH

We are highly successful on international market

Companies are increasingly looking across borders to enter into growing markets and attract strategic capital.  Key to success is strong local business knowledge and in-depth understanding of cultural and legal practices with well trusted partners. To find successful transaction opportunities for our clients we regularly collaborate with our overseas colleagues in alliance with Corporate Finance network.

The alliance is a leading international alliance of investment banks and corporate finance advisory firms with operations in Africa, Asia, Australasia, Europe, the Middle East and North America. The alliance was formed in 2002 and consists of 12 member firms who provide enhanced access to international counter-parties and market intelligence.
